<div class="container-fluid p-5">
  <div class="row mb-3 justify-content-center">
    <div class="col">
      <h3>
        <span class="fs-5"><i class="bi bi-inboxes-fill"></i></span> Request
        <span class="text-success">Dosir</span>
      </h3>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row mb-3 justify-content-center">
    <div class="col">
      <div class="alert alert-success p-4" role="alert">
        <i class="bi bi-chevron-right"></i> Anda belum memiliki riwayat
        permintaan dosir. Tekan tombol <strong>Request Dosir</strong> di bawah
